data.description: PRICE REDUCED+MOTIVATED SELLERS located in Jordan Woods!! This almost 1 year old Farmhouse is where modern comfort meets country living! This immaculate home truly offers the best of both worlds; Spacious open floor plan, perfect for both relaxation and entertaining.. The living room welcomes you with its cozy ambiance- featuring a stunning gas fireplace as its centerpiece.. the kitchen is a culinary delight, boasting sleek quartz countertops with a breakfast bar, white shaker style crowned cabinets which offers ample storage space. The LVT floors throughout add a touch of elegance, along with farm house style windows that flood the entire home with natural light. Retreat to the primary bedroom suite, a sanctuary of comfort which features two walk in closets, double vanity, and walk in shower. The guest bedrooms are similar in size and offer a spacious space, and another full bathroom near by. Additional features of this home include second floor laundry, central air, with a (1) ductless split system for energy efficiency. A partially finished walk out basement awaiting your personal touch, and the potential to easily transition in to a fully finished additional 640 square feet of space!!! Whether you envision a gym, office, entertainment area- the possibilities are endless!! Situated near RT 2, RT 82, I-395, CT Shoreline, Lake Hayward, Mohegan Sun/ Foxwoods Casino & so much more-this home offers unparalleled convenience without compromising on privacy or tranquility!!!! Don't miss out on this rare opportunity to own a one-year-old farmhouse near amenities. Experience the best of countryside living with modern convenience! Never worry about plowing or road maintenance again!
